[package]
name = "iroha"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Iroha 2 team <https://github.com/orgs/soramitsu/teams/iroha2>"]
description = "Iroha is a straightforward distributed ledger technology (DLT), inspired by Japanese Kaizen principle â€” eliminate excessiveness (muri). Iroha has essential functionality for your asset, information and identity management needs, at the same time being an efficient and trustworthy crash fault-tolerant tool for your enterprise needs."
homepage = "https://github.com/hyperledger/iroha/tree/iroha2-dev"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["crypto", "blockchain", "ledger"]
categories = ["cryptography::cryptocurrencies"]
license = "Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/hyperledger/iroha/tree/iroha2-dev"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1"
chrono = "0.4"
rand = "0.7.3"
serde_json = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
ursa = "=0.3.6"
warp = "0.3"

[dependencies.dashmap]
version = "4.0"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.4"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_actor]
path = "../iroha_actor"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_config]
version = "=0.1.0"
path = "../iroha_config"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_crypto]
version = "=0.1.0"
path = "../iroha_crypto"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_data_model]
path = "../iroha_data_model"
features = ["warp"]
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_derive]
version = "=0.1.0"
path = "../iroha_macro/iroha_derive"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_error]
version = "=0.1.0"
path = "../iroha_error"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_futures]
path = "../iroha_futures"

[dependencies.iroha_schema]
path = "../iroha_schema"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.iroha_telemetry]
path = "../iroha_telemetry"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.iroha_version]
version = "=0.1.0"
path = "../iroha_version"
features = ["warp"]
optional = false

[dependencies.parity-scale-codec]
version = "2"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.structopt]
version = "0.3"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.6.0"
features = ["sync", "time", "rt", "io-util", "rt-multi-thread", "macros", "fs"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
version = "0.1.6"
features = ["fs"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
byte-unit = "4.0.12"
criterion = "0.3"
hex = "0.4.0"
hex-literal = "0.2.1"
maplit = "1.0.2"
tempfile = "3"
unique_port = "0.1.0"

[features]
bridge = []
cli = ["structopt"]
default = ["bridge", "cli"]
dev-telemetry = ["iroha_telemetry"]
dex = []
roles = ["iroha_data_model/roles"]
telemetry = []

name = "iroha"
test = true
